Description:
Description
To be able to create documents with more information, new fields should be added to the Vreemdeling proces.

Solution
In process Vreemdeling below field Land, 
add field 'CRV nummer' and ‘IND BES nummer’. 
These new fields should not be mandatory, if a person has a CRV or IND BES number in ACTFMS this can be automatically included. (KPNAPF09G.BVDRCRVN)
Also add the fieldsLuchtvaart maatschappij/ rederij, naam vliegtuig/boot, telefoon nummer Boot/ vliegtuig, Agentschap, Geboorte plaats, telefoon nummer (Thuis, Mobiel en Werk), ticketnummer, PNR nummer, Meereizende minderjarige kinderen. As shown in the screenshot. 
This field should be saved in the same table as now Vreemdeling is saved.

See detailed description and screenshot in attachment.

Testplan
Step 1: Go to Generiek - assistentie - rol/proces - Vreemdeling
Step 2: Add a new vVreemdeling and fill all fields.
Step 3: it should be possible to register CRV nummer, ticketnummer, PNR nummer etc.

Navigation
Generiek - assistentie - rol/proces - Vreemdeling

Description
For the Vremdeling module phase 2 there are some chanes required in the Reisdocument tab.
Tab reisdocument logic will be modified.

Solution
When opening the tab reisdocument user must first select type of Document.(Passport, Visa or Travel Document) for each Travel Document a new record can be added in this tab.
Based on the selection the required fields should show.

See attachment for detailed description and field changes and screenshot.

Testplan
Step 1: Go to Generiek - Assistentie.
Step 2: Go to Rol/proces tab and add a new Vreemdeling proces
Step 3: Select Soort Document Visum.
Step 4: Should be possible to enter Visum Hoofdbestemming "Caribisch Gebied Hoofddoel Curaçao"
Step 5: when filling the mandatory fields record should be saved.
Step 6: Create an additional Reisdocument
Step 7: Select Soort document Paspoort
Step 8: fill in mandatory fields and save record

Description
It should be possible to add additional Toezicht verbalisant in Vreemdeling proces Tab Toegang.

Solution
Add addition the two fields Tozicht Verbalisant in tab Toegang, These two additional fields should contain the same users list as Verbalisant.
When a Werkopdracht is send to these Toegang Verbalisant 1 or Toegang Verbalisant 2, this should also be sent to The Toezicht Verbalisant 1 and Toezicht Verbalisant 2.
Functionality for sending a Werkopdracht will be described in another task.

Test plan
Step 1: Go to generiek - Assistentie open an existing record and add in Rol/proces a Vreemdeling
Step 2: in tab Toegang there should be a possibility to add Toezicht Verbalisant 1 and 2.
Step 3: It should be possible top save this record.

Generiek - Assistentie - Rol/proces - Vreemdeling

Description
For the Vremdeling module phase 2 there are some chanes required in the Weigering tab.
To have additional field to create complete documents.

Solution
In Weigering Tab In Vreemdeling process, the following fields are added in the Weigering tab. Fields: To operator, To telephone, To telefax, Beheerst Nederlandse tijd (ja/nee), Taal verhoor (dropdown) naam Tolk, are processed in the Weigering tab.

Check attachment for detailed description.

Testplan
Step 1: Go to Generiek - Assistentie.
Step 2: Go to Rol/proces tab and add a new Vreemdeling proces
Step 3: Fill in mandatory fields and save
Step 4: Go to Weigering tab and add mandatory fields.
SteP 5: It should be possible to fill in "Telefoon", "Telefax" en "Beheerst Nederlandse taal"
Step 6: It should be possible to save record.

Navigation
Generiek - Asstentie - rol/proces - Vreemdeling - tab Weigering

Possibility to enter, as a Rijbewijs, a Vaarbewijs in ACTPOL at the personen module

 

Make changes to POL0009.pdw to add a new section for Vaarbewijs. Can follow the
logic and copy the HTML from Rijbewijs to implement. Each section is a set of tasks
add/update/delete in the same program. 
Table KPNAPF09C is for the existing vehicle type data, make a new KPNAPF09[new
letter] for the vessel type data. 
File KPSLPF0288 is for new list values. Use this file for the new Vessel License Type
field values/dropdown.
